profile: Electrika focuses solely on home electrical repairs, installation and renovation in the greater Montreal area: downtown, West Island, South Shore and Laval. All our electricians have over 15 years of experience in the electrical industry; they are fully licensed and insured to work in your home with all the diligence it requires.
hours: Mon - Fri 7am - 5pm, Closed Sat and Sun, 24/7 Emergency Service available
